00:00:00.100 --> 00:00:02.200
Welcome to Tarla Dalal's kitchen

00:00:02.200 --> 00:00:03.160
My name is Krupali

00:00:03.200 --> 00:00:06.820
Today i am going to show you a sheera recipe, named Akhrot kaju sheera

00:00:13.140 --> 00:00:15.200
first we will start making the sugar syrup

00:00:23.520 --> 00:00:27.640
cook on a slow flame, for 2 to 3 minutes, stirring it continuously

00:00:28.760 --> 00:00:33.060
now the sugar has completely melted, and started to boil.

00:00:36.620 --> 00:00:38.000
sugar syrup is ready now

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:41.400
keep it to cool slightly and meanwhile, we will start making the sheera.

00:00:41.680 --> 00:00:45.080
for the sheera, heat the ghee in a broad non-stick pan

00:00:54.920 --> 00:00:59.240
saute it on slow flame for 4 to 5 minutes, while stirring it continuously.

00:00:59.680 --> 00:01:02.720
stirring it continuously is very important

00:01:05.078 --> 00:01:07.718
Saute it till it is lightbrown in colour

00:01:12.960 --> 00:01:14.940
the mixture is light brown in colour now

00:01:19.340 --> 00:01:21.620
add the prepared sugar syrup..

00:01:24.480 --> 00:01:25.700
mix very well

00:01:26.580 --> 00:01:29.400
cook on a medium flame for 2 minutes.

00:01:33.740 --> 00:01:35.860
do not forget to stir it continuously.

00:01:39.940 --> 00:01:43.120
our sheera is ready to be served

00:01:47.540 --> 00:01:50.360
Akhrot Kaju Sheera is ready now , enjoy it hot

00:01:50.360 --> 00:01:55.880
in case if you want have  after some time, reheat and serve immediately

00:01:56.060 --> 00:01:57.580
and enjoy this recipe.

